                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t17750111-41-off200 t17750111-41-crimeloc202"></join>, with a lady, I felt a hand between her and me, I turned and saw my handkerchief in the hand of the prisoner, I collared him, but the lady fainting away he got from me, he was stopped by a constable who saw him throw away three or four handkerchiefs, and they were run away with by the mob all but one, which is not mine, I am positive to the man, and am sure I saw my handkerchief in his hand.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence.</p>
               <p>I was further from the gentleman than I am now, there was another person running, the gentleman called stop thief, and I ran after him.</p>
